<title>USA: LSI Logic to buy back up to 5 mln shares.</title>
<headline>LSI Logic to buy back up to 5 mln shares.</headline>
<dateline>MILPITAS, Calif. 1997-07-28</dateline>
<text>
<p>LSI Logic Corp said Monday it plans to buy back up to five million common shares, or about three percent of its outstanding stock.</p>
<p>At the end of June, the company had roughly 145 million shares outstanding, according to its earnings statement.</p>
<p>The company, which was not immediately available for comment, said in a statement it made the buyback decision &quot;in view of the lower price at which the company stock has recently traded.&quot;</p>
